The paper deals with a problem of choosing the best option from a sequence of fluctuating prices, which involves probability theory and decision-making. This suggests that the paper may belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the classical secretary problem, which is a well-known problem in Game Theory (cs.GT) and Mathematics (cs.MA). Therefore, these sub-categories are also likely candidates.
